<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Authentication Error - TV Station</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .error-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .error-icon {
            font-size: 64px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .error-header h1 {
            color: #ef4444;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .error-header p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .error-box {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .error-box h3 {
            color: #7f1d1d;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .error-code {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #7f1d1d;
            word-break: break-all;
        }

        .error-description {
            color: #7f1d1d;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .details-section {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .details-section h4 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .detail-item {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            padding: 5px 0;
            word-break: break-all;
        }

        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
            display: inline-block;
            min-width: 100px;
        }

        .buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }

        button {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #5568d3;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: #e5e7eb;
            color: #333;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #d1d5db;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .help-section {
            background: #f0f4ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #444;
        }

        .help-section strong {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #333;
        }

        ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="error-header">
            <div class="error-icon">⚠️</div>
            <h1>Authentication Error</h1>
            <p>Something went wrong during the login process</p>
        </div>

        <div class="error-box">
            <h3>Error Code</h3>
            <div class="error-code">
                <%= error || 'UNKNOWN_ERROR' %>
            </div>

            <% if (error_description) { %>
                <h3 style="margin-top: 15px;">Error Details</h3>
                <div class="error-description">
                    <%= error_description %>
                </div>
                <% } %>
        </div>

        <% if (error==='invalid_scope' ) { %>
            <div class="details-section">
                <h4>What Happened?</h4>
                <p style="color: #666; font-size: 13px;">
                    The TV Station App requested access scopes that your Ping Federate client is not configured to use.
                    Only the default scope can be requested for this client.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="help-section">
                <strong>How to Fix This:</strong>
                <ol>
                    <li>Contact your Ping Federate administrator</li>
                    <li>Ask to update the <strong>
                            <%= clientId || 'tv-station-client' %>
                        </strong> OAuth client</li>
                    <li>Ensure it allows the <code>openid profile email</code> scopes</li>
                    <li>Try logging in again</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            <% } else if (error==='access_denied' ) { %>
                <div class="help-section">
                    <strong>You Denied Access</strong>
                    <p style="margin-top: 8px;">
                        You clicked "Cancel" or "Deny" during the authorization process.
                        Please approve access to your information to continue.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <% } else if (error==='invalid_client' ) { %>
                    <div class="help-section">
                        <strong>Client Configuration Error</strong>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Verify the TV Station App client credentials in Ping Federate</li>
                            <li>Ensure the redirect URI is correctly configured</li>
                            <li>Expected: <code><%= redirectUri || 'http://localhost:3001/auth/callback' %></code></li>
                            <li>Contact your administrator if the issue persists</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <div class="help-section">
                            <strong>Troubleshooting Steps:</strong>
                            <ol>
                                <li>Clear your browser cookies and cache</li>
                                <li>Try again in an incognito/private window</li>
                                <li>Check that Ping Federate is accessible and running</li>
                                <li>Contact your administrator if the problem continues</li>
                            </ol>
                        </div>
                        <% } %>

                            <% if (state) { %>
                                <div class="details-section" style="margin-top: 20px;">
                                    <h4>Request Information</h4>
                                    <div class="detail-item">
                                        <span class="detail-label">State:</span>
                                        <code><%= state %></code>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="detail-item">
                                        <span class="detail-label">Client:</span>
                                        <code><%= clientId || 'tv-station-client' %></code>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="detail-item">
                                        <span class="detail-label">Timestamp:</span>
                                        <code><%= new Date().toISOString() %></code>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <% } %>

                                    <div class="buttons">
                                        <a href="/" style="text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center;">
                                            <button class="btn-primary">← Back to Home</button>
                                        </a>
                                        <a href="/auth/login"
                                            style="text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center;">
                                            <button class="btn-secondary">Try Again</button>
                                        </a>
                                    </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>